1
00:01:43,320 --> 00:01:44,450
What's on your mind?

2
00:01:44,759 --> 00:01:46,289
You seem so lost in thought.

3
00:01:47,880 --> 00:01:50,320
I was just thinking about having a drink, and here you are.

4
00:01:50,320 --> 00:01:52,120
You really are a kindred spirit.

5
00:01:52,320 --> 00:01:53,200
Then I'll

6
00:01:54,600 --> 00:01:57,000
keep you company. Let's drink till we drop.

7
00:01:57,240 --> 00:01:57,700
Cheers.

8
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:58,479
Cheers.

9
00:02:07,320 --> 00:02:08,650
What are your plans now?

10
00:02:09,560 --> 00:02:11,420
I feel so relieved all of a sudden.

11
00:02:11,520 --> 00:02:13,320
I don't know where to go, though.

12
00:02:13,560 --> 00:02:15,520
If you want to go back to the Xiao Army,

13
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:16,760
I'll go with you.

14
00:02:18,320 --> 00:02:20,320
The Xiao family has served in the army for generations.

15
00:02:20,320 --> 00:02:21,000
Let it end

16
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:22,680
with me.

17
00:02:26,920 --> 00:02:29,450
Then why not go to Jiangnan with General Xiao?

18
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:30,250
You once said

19
00:02:30,760 --> 00:02:32,490
that you really like Jiangnan.

20
00:02:38,920 --> 00:02:39,520
Li Yunmo.

21
00:02:40,640 --> 00:02:41,440
Do you think

22
00:02:42,600 --> 00:02:44,200
hatred can ever be resolved?

23
00:02:48,840 --> 00:02:49,400
So,

24
00:02:50,240 --> 00:02:52,100
you still can't let go of Li Yunxi.

25
00:02:52,880 --> 00:02:54,680
You want to return to the palace.

26
00:02:55,920 --> 00:02:56,560
You...

27
00:02:57,079 --> 00:02:58,200
you're sensitive,

28
00:02:58,440 --> 00:02:59,400
considerate,

29
00:02:59,920 --> 00:03:01,160
free-spirited, and kind.

30
00:03:01,160 --> 00:03:02,290
You're too perfect.

31
00:03:09,480 --> 00:03:11,410
Actually, I'm not free-spirited,

32
00:03:11,720 --> 00:03:12,400
kind,

33
00:03:13,520 --> 00:03:14,240
or perfect.

34
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:16,290
Who would believe that?

35
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:17,480
Even as a friend,

36
00:03:17,640 --> 00:03:18,970
you're so considerate.

37
00:03:19,120 --> 00:03:21,640
The one you love will surely

38
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:23,930
have you wrapped around their finger.

39
00:03:24,720 --> 00:03:25,800
I already am.

40
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:27,079
What?

41
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:28,840
Xiao Ling.

42
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:33,320
I'm only considerate

43
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:35,760
and patient with you.

44
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:38,560
My perfection is just

45
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:40,140
a disguise in front of you.

46
00:03:41,920 --> 00:03:43,680
Because you are the one I love.

47
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:51,090
What are you talking about?

48
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:52,880
We are good brothers.

49
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:55,680
We spent years in the military camp together.

50
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:57,320
We fought side by side and talked about everything.

51
00:03:57,320 --> 00:03:59,520
I even followed you back to the capital.

52
00:04:00,800 --> 00:04:01,320
Before,

53
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:03,340
you only had eyes for Li Yunxi.

54
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:10,440
Now,

55
00:04:13,640 --> 00:04:15,200
will you give me a chance?

56
00:04:41,720 --> 00:04:42,520
Your Majesty,

57
00:04:42,960 --> 00:04:45,680
The Empress didn't return to the Xiao Army camp,

58
00:04:46,240 --> 00:04:48,560
nor did she follow the General to Jiangnan.

59
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:50,360
She never left.

60
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:54,340
Aling is still in the capital.

61
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:06,160
Are you really leaving, My Lady?

62
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:10,440
I know full well

63
00:05:10,440 --> 00:05:12,100
that I cannot be with Li Yunmo.

64
00:05:13,120 --> 00:05:14,720
I cannot give him false hope.

65
00:05:28,440 --> 00:05:29,640
To my wife, Xiao Ling,

66
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:32,200
though we part today,

67
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:34,460
my heart remains with you.

68
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:36,560
Until the end of time,

69
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:38,880
my love will never waver.

70
00:05:40,600 --> 00:05:42,060
I toss and turn in longing.

71
00:05:42,640 --> 00:05:44,300
I only hope to reunite one day.

72
00:05:45,440 --> 00:05:47,240
And never part until we are gray.

73
00:05:52,440 --> 00:05:54,040
This is not a divorce letter,

74
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:56,240
but a love letter.

75
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:10,500
That is my petal water.

76
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:12,280
If Your Majesty wishes to soak,

77
00:06:12,280 --> 00:06:13,280
go to Feixue Hall.

78
00:06:23,080 --> 00:06:24,010
Stop rushing me.

79
00:06:24,720 --> 00:06:26,120
I will go back right away.

80
00:06:27,560 --> 00:06:28,890
I am not here to rush you.

81
00:06:33,400 --> 00:06:34,080
Ling.

82
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:38,159
You came back.

83
00:06:43,840 --> 00:06:45,440
Since it is a mutual divorce,

84
00:06:45,640 --> 00:06:47,500
both husband and wife must agree.

85
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:50,210
I did have selfish motives.

86
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:53,960
I hope that after reading this letter,

87
00:06:53,960 --> 00:06:55,360
you will change your mind

88
00:06:57,520 --> 00:06:59,120
and come back to me.

89
00:07:02,720 --> 00:07:03,650
There are things

90
00:07:04,880 --> 00:07:06,810
that I may never be able to let go of.

91
00:07:12,920 --> 00:07:13,920
But marrying you,

92
00:07:15,400 --> 00:07:16,400
I don't regret it.

93
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:24,860
You were right.

94
00:07:25,960 --> 00:07:27,800
Even if we torment each other,

95
00:07:29,200 --> 00:07:31,260
we must stay together for a lifetime.

96
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:33,740
we'll torment each other for a lifetime.

97
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:37,480
I came back to tell you

98
00:07:39,080 --> 00:07:40,810
that I won't agree to a divorce.

99
00:07:41,560 --> 00:07:42,960
Neither of us can escape.

100
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:46,200
We'll be together even in death.

101
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:04,120
Good.

102
00:08:13,920 --> 00:08:14,380
Master.

103
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:24,640
Do it.

104
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:25,800
I understand.

105
00:08:39,600 --> 00:08:40,159
Hanxing.

106
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:42,640
Hanxing.

107
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:47,010
Hanxing.

108
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:50,840
Doctor!

109
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:52,360
Doctor!

110
00:09:32,840 --> 00:09:34,240
So it was you who sent me the news

111
00:09:34,240 --> 00:09:36,440
that the Empress left the palace early.

112
00:09:39,320 --> 00:09:40,000
Do it.

113
00:09:40,520 --> 00:09:41,320
I understand.

114
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:50,500
If Your Highness won't leave,

115
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:53,490
I'll have to threaten you with my life.

116
00:09:53,720 --> 00:09:55,650
I can't let anything happen to you.

117
00:09:55,880 --> 00:09:57,810
You're the only family I have left.

118
00:09:58,400 --> 00:10:00,260
I'll protect you, no matter what.

119
00:10:02,520 --> 00:10:03,240
Master.

120
00:10:15,160 --> 00:10:16,240
That scent again.

121
00:10:21,920 --> 00:10:23,250
I've been reborn again.

122
00:10:26,680 --> 00:10:27,600
Hanxing.

123
00:10:28,560 --> 00:10:29,840
I never suspected you.

124
00:10:30,480 --> 00:10:31,880
What are you really up to?

125
00:10:41,040 --> 00:10:42,960
Your Highness, you're sweating.

126
00:10:43,280 --> 00:10:44,680
Did you have a nightmare?

127
00:10:48,240 --> 00:10:49,640
I never noticed before.

128
00:10:50,280 --> 00:10:52,140
The way Hanxing holds that duster

129
00:10:52,640 --> 00:10:54,700
makes her look like a martial artist.

130
00:10:54,760 --> 00:10:55,620
Your Highness,

131
00:10:55,880 --> 00:10:57,810
why are you looking at me like that?

132
00:10:58,880 --> 00:10:59,680
It's nothing.

133
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:02,400
My chest feels tight.

134
00:11:04,040 --> 00:11:05,160
Pour me some tea.

135
00:11:05,240 --> 00:11:06,840
Yes. I'll make you some tea.

136
00:11:21,040 --> 00:11:21,900
Your Highness,

137
00:11:22,120 --> 00:11:24,280
His Majesty is hosting a banquet at Qinghuan Pavilion tonight.

138
00:11:24,280 --> 00:11:25,680
He invites you to attend.

139
00:11:26,480 --> 00:11:27,240
Go tell him

140
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:29,290
that I am unwell tonight

141
00:11:29,720 --> 00:11:31,160
and cannot attend the banquet.

142
00:11:31,160 --> 00:11:31,680
Yes.

143
00:11:36,560 --> 00:11:37,420
Your Highness,

144
00:11:39,320 --> 00:11:41,160
don't hurt yourself. Let me clean it up.
